column4: How well is the problem identified and defined?
column5: What is the level of pain area felt / perceived by the target customers / consumers?
column6: What is the level of uniqueness in the proposition for the venture?
column7: How high are the defensible technology barriers in the business? (High being 4)
column8: What is the strength of the competitive advantage in the business model?
column9: What is the level of competition in terms of alternatives available ?
column10: What is the level of sustainability of the competitive advantage in the next 24 months?
column11: Are the business milestones for the next 24 months exciting?
column12: Are the business metrics clearly defined
column13: How feasible do you think is the Go To Market plan in next 12-18 month timeframe ?
column14: What is the level of understanding and clarity of the financial projections by the team ?
column15: Does the business model has high level of operating leverage & scalability potential ?
column16: How do you think is the ability of the team to manage risks with Plan B ?
column17: What would you say is your ‘Unfair Advantage’ that would add competitive advantage vs anyone who could start the same venture ?
column18: How would you rate the likability & connect with the Founder and his authenticity?
column19: How did you find the overall presentation quality in terms of clarity and impact through communication ?
column20: How would you rate the quality of presentation deck in terms of clarity, scope, visual impact & simplicity ?
column21: What is the overall feasibility of the business going forward ?
